dct_title_s: Plan regulador metropolitano de Santiago : incorpora a la provincia de Chacabuco
dct_description_sm: Includes index. On verso: Proposal for the incorporation of Chacabuco province to the "Plan regulador metropolitano de Santiago." Includes 5 maps to support this proposal.
dct_creator_sm: Chile. Ministerio de Vivienda y Urbanismo
